skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: one twenty quotes
des:
Start your day with inspirational, no nonsense, health and fitness inspired quotes from the 120 day fat to fit - 120FTF - program. 

When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
